class Solution(object):
    def findComplement(self, num):
        i = 1
        while num >= i:
            num ^= i
            i <<= 1
        return num
```
2. Find the bit length (say L) and flip num by **num ^ 11...1**   (L ones).
```
    def findComplement(self, num):
        return num ^ ((1<<num.bit_length())-1)
```
