* Convert the decimal string back to integer number.
```
public int findComplement(int num) {
        String comp = "";
        while(num != 0){
            if(num%2 == 1) comp = '0'+comp;
            else comp = '1'+comp;
            num/= 2;
        }

        int res = 0;
        for(int i=comp.length()-1; i>=0; i--){
            int temp = comp.charAt(i)-'0';
            res+= temp*Math.pow(2, comp.length()-i-1);
        }
        return res;
    }
```
